One of the nearest masjid's of IGI airport, New Delhi. Masjid is situated near main road, it is easily accessible. You can park your vehicle in the side of the main road or you can park it infront of the masjid. But the space is very small, maybe for two three cars. Masjid is very spacious, around 200 people can pray at a time.

Washroom is also there and hot water is available during winter season.
